name: I Flew on Japan Airlines' Boeing 767!
description:
Back in May, I spent a week in Japan with a couple friends after flying there on WestJet's inaugural flight from Calgary.

That wasn't the only interesting flight we took on that trip though, and after spending a day in Tokyo, we hopped on board a Japan Airlines 767 to Hiroshima. Let's see what a Japanese domestic flight is like!
